---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="C-Clamp CAD Model and Failure Analysis"
  description="Reconstructed and analyzed a C-clamp using finite element analysis."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>

    <h1>C-Clamp CAD Model and Failure Analysis</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Reconstructed a C-clamp CAD model and performed finite element analysis
      to identify failure points.
    </p>

    <img
      src="/images/projects/c-clamp.jpg"
      alt="C-Clamp CAD Model and Failure Analysis"
    />
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>

    <p>
      This project involved reverse engineering a physical C-clamp and
      evaluating its structural performance under load.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Process</h2>

    <p>
      Precision measurements were used to create a 1:1 CAD model, which was
      then analyzed using finite element methods to identify stress
      concentrations and failure locations.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tools Used</h2>

    <p>SOLIDWORKS • FEA • Simulation</p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 24px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  section + section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
</style>